tab leveey utt khde hua, arthata kahaatiyon men se amasaai ka putra mahat, aur ajaryah ka putra yoael, aur marariyon men se abdee ka putra keesha, aur yahallelel ka putra ajaryah, aur geshaniyon men se jimma ka putra yoah, aur yoah ka putra aedena.
parantu kis kee itanee shaktai haai, ki usake liye bhvan banaa, vah to svarga men varan sab se unche svarga men bhee naheen samata? maain kya hoo ki usake samhane dhoop jalane ko chhod aur kisee manasa se usaka bhvan banaun?
bahut se logon ne arthata aepraaim, manashsho, issakar aur jabooloon men se bahuton ne apane ko shuuddh naheen kiya tha, taubhee ve fasah ke pashu ka mans likhee hui vidhai ke viruddh khate the. kyonkee hijaakiyyah ne unake liye yah praarthna kee thee, ki yahova jo bhla haai, vah un sabhon ke pap ddhanp de
aur jo jo kam us ne parameshvar ke bhvan kee upasana aur vyavastha aur agyaa ke vishay apane parameshvar kee khoj men kiya, vah us ne apana sara man lagakar kiya aur us men kratarth bhee hua.
usee hijaakiyyah ne geehon nam nadee ke upar ke sote ko pattkar us nadee ko neeche kee or daudapur kee paachchhim alang ko seedha pahunchaya, aur hijaakiyyah apane sab kamon men kratarth hota tha.
us ne vah kiya jo yahova kee draashtti men tteek haai, aur jin magan par usaka moolapurush daud chalata raha, unheen par vah bhee chala karata tha aur us se n to daahinee or mooda, aur n bain ora.
aur us ne un sabhon se jo yarooshalem men aur binyameen men the vaaisee hee vacha bandhaai. aur yarooshalem ke nivasee, parameshvar jo unake pitaron ka parameshvar tha, usakee vacha ke anusar karane lage.
jab yahoahaj rajy karane laga, tab vah teis varsha ka tha, aur teen maheene tak yarooshalem men rajy karata raha.
aur sone kee keelon ka taul pachas shokel tha. aur us ne attariyon ko bhee sone se maddhvaya.
aur chokhe sone kee kaainachiya, kattore, dhoopadan aur karachhe banavaae. fir bhvan ke dar aur param pavitra sthan ke bheetaree kivad aur bhvan arthata maandair ke kivad sone ke bane.
isaliye ab he israaael ke parameshvar yahova is vachan ko bhee moora kar, jo too ne apane das mere pita daud ko diya tha, ki tere kul men mere samhane israaael kee gaee par virajanevale sada bane rahenge, yah ho ki jaaise too apane ko mere sammukh janakar chalata raha, vaaise hee tere vansh ke log apanee chal chalan men aeesee chaukasee kare, ki meree yyavastha par chalen.
tab sab praja samet raja ne yahova ko bali chaddhai.
tab sulaaiman ne yahova kee us vedee par jo us ne osare ke age banai thee, yahova ko homabali chaddhai.
aur ve praati varsha apanee apanee bhentt arthata chandee aur sone ke patra, vasr-shasr, sugandhadrayy, ghaede aur khchchar le ate the.
maain to samajhta hama, ki maain kisee bat men bade se bade praeriton se kam naheen hoon.
maain maseeh men aek manushy ko janata hoo, chaudah varsha huae ki n jane dehasahit, n jane deharaahit, parameshvar janata haai, aeesa manushy teesare svarga tak utta liya gaya.
nidan, he bhaiyo, anaandait raho siddh banate jao ddhaddhs rakho aek hee man rakho mel se raho, aur praem aur shaaantai ka data parameshvar tumhare sath hoga.
aur maain ne yahee bat tumhen isaliye likhee, ki kaheen aeesa n ho, ki mere ane par jin se anand milana chahia, maain un se udas houn kyonaki mujhe tum sab par is bat ka bhrosa haai, ki jo mera anand haai, vahee tum sab ka bhee haai.
parantu jab kabhee un ka day prabhu kee or firega, tab vah parada utt jaaega.
kyonaki avashy haai, ki ham sab ka hal maseeh ke nyay asan ke samhane khul jaa, ki har aek vyaaktai apane apane bhle bure kamon ka badala jo us ne deh ke dara kiae hon paae..
so he pyaro jab ki ye pratigyaaaen hamen milee haai, to ao, ham apane ap ko shareer aur atma kee sab malinata shuuddh kare, aur parameshvar ka bhy rakhte huae paavitrata ko siddh karen..
jesa likha haai, ki jis ne bahut battora usaka kuchh aadhaik n nikala aur jis ne thoda battora usaka kuchh kam n nikala..
aur praem yah haai ki ham us kee agyaaon ke anusar chalen: yah vahee agyaa haai, jo tum ne arambh se sunee haai aur tumhen is par chalana bhee chahiae.
tab yehoo rekab ke putra yahonadab ko sang lekar bal ke bhpan men gaya, aur bal ke upasakon se kaha, ddoonddhkar dekho, ki yahan tumhare sang yahova ka koi upasak to naheen haai, keval bal hee ke upasak haain.
tab yahoyada ne yahova ke, aur raja-praja ke beech yahova kee praja hone kee vacha bandhaai, aur us ne raja aur praja ke madhy bhee vacha bandhaai.
isaliye yahova ne israaael ko aek chhudanevala diya aur ve aram ke vash se choott gaae aur israaaelee agale dinon kee nai fir apane apane dere men rahane lage.
too ne aedomiyon ko jeeta to haai isaaliye too fool utta haai. usee par badai parata hua ghar rah ja too apanee haani ke liye yahan kyon hath uttata haai, jis se too kya varan yahooda bhee teecha khaaega ?
jakaryah ke aur kam israaael ke rajaon ke itihas kee pustak men likhe haain.
parantu vah israaael ke rajaon kee see chal chala, varan un jaatiyon ke ghainaune kamon ke anusar, jinhen yahova ne israaaeliyon ke samhane se desh se nikal diya tha, us ne apane bette ko bhee ag men hom kar diya.
taubhee yahova ne sab bhvishyadvktaon aur sab dashairyon ke dara israaael aur yahooda ko yah kah kar chitaya tha, ki apanee buree chal chhodkar us saree yyavastha ke anusar jo maain ne tumhare purakhaon ko dee thee, aur apane das bhavishyadvktaon ke hath toomhare pas pahunchai haai, meree agyaaon aur vidhaiyon ko mana karo.
jab vah rajy karane laga tab pachchees varsha ka tha, aur unatees varsha tak yarooshalem men rajy karata raha. aur usakee mata ka nam abee tha, jo jakaryah kee bettee thee.
tab maain akar tum ko aeese desh men le jaunga, jo tumhare desh ke saman anaj aur naye dakhmadha ka desha, rottee aur dakhbariyon ka desha, jalapaiyon aur madha ka desh haai, vahan tum maroge nahee, jeevit rahoge to jab hijaakiyyah yah kahakar tum ko bahakaa, ki yahova ham ko bachaaega, tab usakee n sunana.
kya too ne naheen suna, ki praacheenakal se maain ne yahee ttharaya? aur agale dinon se isakee taaiyaree kee thee, unhen ab maain ne poora bhee kiya haai, ki too gaddhvale nagaron ko khndhar hee khndhar kar de,
ahajyah ke aur kam jo us ne kiae vah kya israaael ke rajaon ke itihas kee pustak men naheen likhe haain?
parantu unhon ne n mana, baran manashsho ne unako yahan tak bhttka diya ki unhon ne un jatiyon se bhee baddhkar burai kee jinhen yahova ne israaaeliyon ke samhane se vinash kiya tha.
ki yah pustak jo milee haai, usakee baton ke vishy tum jakar meree or praja kee aur sab sahoodiyon kee or se yahova se poochho, kyonaki yahova kee badee hee jalajalahatt ham par is karan bhdkee haai, ki hamare purakhaon ne is pustak kee baten n manee ki kuchh hamare liye likha haai, usake anusar karate.
raja yoshaiyyah ke attarahaven varsha men yahova ke liye yarooshalem men yah fasah mana gaya.
aur sab dhanavan jo sat hajar the, aur kareegar aur lohar jo milakar aek hajar the, aur ve sab veer aur yuddh ke yogy the, unhen babel ka raja bandhaua karake babel ko le gaya.
tab kya chhotte kya bade saree praja ke log aur dalon ke pradhaan kasadiyon ke dr ke mare uttkar misra men jakar rahane lage.
yahooda ke raja yahoshaapat ke attarahaven varsha men ahab ka putra yahoram shaimaron men rajy karane laga, aur barah parsha tak rajy karata raha.
fir too apane betton samet apane ghar men ja, aur dar band karaken un sab baratanon men tel undel dena, aur jo bhr jaae unhen alag rakhna.
tab vah chaddhkar ladke par is reeati se lett gaya ki apana munh usake munh se aur apanee ankhen usakee ankhon se aur apane hath usake hathon se mila diye aur vah ladke par pasar gaya, tab ladke kee deh garma hone lagee.
vah usake yahan se thodee door jala gaya tha, ki parameshvar ke bhkt aeleesha ka sevak gehajee sochane laga, ki mere svamee ne to us aramee naman ko aeesa hee chhod diya haai ki jo vah le aya tha usako us ne n liya, parantu yahova ke jeevan kee shapath maain usake peechhe daudkar us se kuchh n kuchh le loonga.
tab us ne unake liye badee jevanar kee, aur jab ve kha pee chuke, tab us ne unhen bida kiya, aur ve apane svamee ke pas chale gaae. isake bad aram ke dal israaael ke desh men fir n aae.
so usake sath tteek vaaisa hee hua, ataaev vah faattk men logon ke panvon ke neeche dabakar mar gaya.
tab aeleesha bhavishyadvkta ne bhavishyadvktaon ke chelon men se aek ko bulakar us se kaha, kamar bandha, aur hath men tel kee yah kuppee lekar gilad ke ramot ko ja.
jab yehoo faattk men hokar a raha tha tab us ne kaha, he apane svamee ke ghaat karane vale jimrae, kya kushal haai?
aur ve lobh ke liye baten gaddhkar tumhen apane labh ka karan banaaenge, aur jo dand kee agyaa un par paahile se ho chukee haai, usake ane men kuchh bhee der nahee, aur un ka vinash unghata naheen.
to jab ki ye sab vastue, is reeti se pighalanevalee haai, to tumhen pavitra chalachalan aur bhktai men kaaise manushy hona chaahiae.
tab daud ne doot bhejakar use bulava liya aur vah daud ke pas ai, aur vah usake sath soya. vah to retu se shuuddh ho gai thee tab vah apane ghar lautt gai.
tab natan ne daud se kaha, too hee vah manushy haai. israaael ka parameshvar yahova yon kahata haai, ki maain ne tera abhaishok karake tujhe israaael ka raja ttharaya, aur maain te tujhe shaaul ke hath se bachaya
aur amnon lettkar beemar bana aur jab raja use dekhne aya, tab amnon ne raja se kaha, meree baahin tamar akar mere dekhte do pooree banaa, ki maain usake hath se khaun.
vah kah hee chuka tha, ki rajakumar pahunch gaa, aur chilla chillakar rone lage aur raja bhee apane sab karmachariyon samet bilakh bilakh kar rone laga.
aur abashaalom ke teen bette, aur tamar nam aek bettee utpann hui thee aur yah roopavatee sree thee.
tab kya dekhne men aya, ki sadok bhee aur usake sang sab leveey parameshvar kee vacha ka sandook uttaae huae haain aur unhon ne parameshvar ke sandook ko dhar diya, tab aebyatar chaddha, aur jab tak sab log nagar se n nikale tab tak vaheen raha.
abashaalom ne us se kaha, kya yah teree praeeati haai jo too apane mitra se rakhta haai? too apane mitra ke sang kyon naheen gaya?
daud to mahanaaim men pahuncha. aur abashaalom sab israaaelee purushaen samet yaradan ke par gaya.
jab paharuae ne pukarake raja ko yah bata diya, tab raja ne kaha, yaadi akela ata ho, to sandesha lata hoga. vah daudte daudte nikal aya.
daud ne kaha, he sarooyah ke betto, mujhe tum se kya kam, ki tum aj mere virodhaee tthare ho? aj kya israaael men kisee ko praan dand milega? kya maain naheen janata ki aj maain israaael ka raja hua hoo?
us ne mujh se kaha, mere pas khda hokar mujhe mar dala kyonki mera sir to ghauma jata haai, parantu praan nahee nikalata.
amasa to sadk ke madhy apane lohoo men lott raha tha. to jab us manushy ne dekha ki sab log khde ho gaae haai, tab amasa ko sadk par se maaidan men utta le gaya, aur jab dekha ki jitane usake pas ate haain ve khde ho jate haai, tab us ne usake upar aek kapada dal diya.
tab yishabobanob, jo rapai ke vansh ka tha, aur usake bhale ka fal taul men teen sau shokel peetal ka tha, aur vah nai talavar bandho huae tha, us ne daud ko marane ko ttana.
aur maain usake sath khra bana raha, aur adharma se apane ko bachaae raha, jis men mere fansane ka dr tha.
israaael ke parameshvar ne kaha haai, israaael kee chattan ne mujh se baten kee haai, ki manushyon men prabhuta karanevala aek dhama hoga, jo parameshvar ka bhy manata hua prabhuta karega,
pahadee shamma, araree shaarar ka putra aheeam,
raja ne arauna se kaha, aeesa nahee, maai ye vastuen tujh se avashy dam dekar loonga maain apane parameshvar yahova ko sentament ke homabaali naheen chaddhane ka. so daud ne khalihan aur baailon ko chandee ke pachas shokel pen mol liya.
aur abner apane janon samet usee din ratonrat araba se hokar gaya aur yaradan ke par ho samast bitraen desh men hokar mahanaaim men pahuncha.
jab abner hebraen ko lautt aya, tab yoab us se aekant men baten karane ke liye usako faattk ke bheetar alag le gaya, aur vahan apane bhai asahel ke koon ke palatte men usake pett men aeesa mara ki vah mar gaya.
tab raja ne apane janon ko sath liae huae yarooshalem ko jakar yaboosiyon par chaddhai kee, jo us desh ke nivasee the. unhon ne yah samajhkar, ki daud yahan paaitt n sakega, us se kaha, jab tak too andhon aur langadon ko door n kare, tab tak yahan paaittne n paaega.
aur yahova ka sandook gatee obededom ke ghar men teen maheene raha aur yahova ne obededom aur usake samast gharane ko ashaish dee.
tab daud raja bheetar jakar yahova ke sammukh baaitta, aur kahane laga, he prabhu yahova, kya kahoo, aur mera gharana kya haai, ki too ne mujhe yahan tak pahuncha diya haai?
daud ne poochha, kya shaaul ke gharane men se koi ab tak bacha haai, jisako maain yonatan ke karan praeeati dikhaun?
aur ab tum us vastu ko janate ho, jo use rok rahee haai, ki vah apane hee samay men pragatt ho.
paulus kee or se jo us jeevan kee praatigyaa ke anusar jo maseeh yeeshu men haai, parameshvar kee ichchha se maseeh yeeshu ka praearit haai.
yaadi ham avishvasee bhee hon taubhee vah vishvasayogy bana rahata haai, kyonaki vah ap apana inkar naheen kar sakata..
taaki parameshvar ka jan siddh bane, aur har aek bhle kam ke liye tatpar ho jaae..
maain ashadod ke rahanevalon ko aur ashkalon ke rajadanddhaaree ko bhee nash karoonga maain apana hath aekron ke virooddh chalaunga, aur shosh palishtee log nash honge, parameshvar yahova ka yahee vachan haai..
isee prakar se prabhu yahova apane das bhvishyadvktaon par apana marma bina prakatt kiae kuchh bhee n karega.
vah turant hee balavant ko vinash kar deta, aur gaddh ka bhee satyanash karata haai..
kya ghaede chattan par dauden? kya koi aeese sthan men baailon se joten jahan tum logon ne nyay ko vish se, aur dharma ke fal ko kadve fal se badal dala haai?
parameshvar yahova kee yah vanee haai, dekho, aeese din ate haai, jab maain is desh men mahangee karoonga us men ne to ann kee bookh aur n panee kee pyas hogee, parantu yahova ke vachanon ke sunane hee kee bookh pyas hogee.
parantu tujhe uchit n tha ki too apane bhai ke din me, arthata usakee vipaati ke din men usakee or dekhta rahata, aur yahoodiyon ke nash hone ke din unake upar anand karata, aur unake sankatt ke din bada bol bolata.
tab maain ne kaha, maain tere samhane se nikal diya gaya hoon taubhee tere pavitra maandair kee or fir takoonga.
kayonaki dek, yahova apane paavitrasthan se bahar nikal raha haai, aur vah utarakar prathvee ke unche sthanon par chalega.
ve us samay yahova kee dohai denge, parantu vah unakee n sunega, varan us samay vah unake bure kamon ke karan un se munh fael lega..
tera hath tere draehiyon par pade, aur tere sab shatra nash ho jaaen..
he meree baaiarin, mujh par anand mat kara kyonki jyonhee maain giroonga tyonhee utoonga aur jyonhee maain andhakar men paoonga tyonahi yahova mere liye jyoti ka kam dega.
usake shoorapeeron kee ddhalen lal rang se rangee gai, aur usake yoddha lal rang ke vasr paahine huae haain. taaiyaree ke din rathon ka loha ag kee nai chamakata haai, aur bhale hilaae jate haain.
bharee vachan jisako habakkook nabee ne darshan men paya..
kyonaki prathvee yahova kee mahima ke gyaan se aeesee bhr jaaegee jaaise samudra jal se bhr jata haai..
jo log apane apane ghar kee chht par akash ke gan ko dandvata karate huae yahova kee seva karane kee shapath khate haain
us ne meree naheen sunee, us ne tadna se bhee naheen mana, us ne yahova par bhrosa naheen rakha, vah apane parameshvar ke sameep naheen ai..
tab shaalateeael ke putra jaroobbabel aur yahosadak ke putra yahoshoo mahayajak ne sab bache huae logon samet apane paramashevar yahova kee bat manee aur jo vachan unake parameshvar yahova ne un se kahane ke liye haggaai bhavishyadvkta ko bhej diya tha, use unhon ne man liya aur logon ne yahova ka bhy mana.
usee men se kone ka patthr, usee men se koonttee, usee men se yuddh ka dhanusha, usee men se sab pradhaan pragatt honge.
tab yahooda ke adhaipaati sochenge ki yarooshalem ke nivasee apane parameshvar, senaon ke yahova kee sahayata se mere sahayak banenge..
aur jitanee jatiyon ne yarooshalem se yuddh kiya haai un sabhon ko yahova aeesee mar se marega, ki khde khde unaka mans sad jaaega, aur unakee ankhen apane golakon men sad jaaengee, aur unakee jeebh unake munh men sad jaaegee.
tab maain ne poochha, ye kya karane ko aae haain? us ne kaha, ye ve hee seeng haai, jinhon ne yahooda ko aeesa titara-abitar kiya ki koi sir n utta saka parantu ye log unhen bhgane ke liye aur un jaatiyon ke seengon ko katt dalane ke liye aae haain jinhon ne yahooda ke desh ko titara-abitar karane ke liye unake virooddh apane apane seeng uttaae the..
he bade pahad, too kya haai? jaroobbabel ke samhane too maaidan ho jaaega aur vah chottee ka patthr yah pukarate huae aaega, us par anugrah ho, anugraha!
aur us se yah kah, senaon ka yahova yon kahata haai, us puroosh ko dekh jis ka nam shaakh haai, vah apane hee sthan se ugakar yahova ke maandair ko banaaega.
aur he yahooda ke gharane, aur israael ke gharane, jis prakar tum anyajatiyon ke beech shaap ke karan the usee prakar maain tumhara uddhar karoonga, aur tum ashaeesh ke karan hoge. isaaliye tum mat dro, aur n tumhare hath ddheele padne paaen..
taubhee maain ne yakoob se praem kiya parantu aesav ko aapiry janakar usake pahadon ko ujad dala, aur usakee bapautee ko jangal ke geedadon ka kar diya haai.
parantu usake ane ke din kee kaun sah sakega? aur jab vah dikhai de, tab kaun khda rah sakega? kyonki vah sonar kee ag aur dhaebee ke sabun ke saman haai.
isaliye aeeson ka svagat karana chahia, jis se ham bhee saty ke paksha men un ke sahakarmee hon..
chela apane guroo se bada naheen aur n das apane svamee se.
yoohanna bapaatisma denevale ke dinon se ab tak svarga ke rajy par jor hota raha haai, aur balaval use chheen lete haain.
bhla, manushy ka mooly bhed se kitana baddh kar haai isaaliye sabt ke din bhlai karana uchit haai: tab us ne us manushy se kaha, apana hath baddha.
daakkhian kee ranee nyay ke din is yug ke logon ke sath uttkar unhen doshaee ttharaaegee, kyonaki vah sulaaiman ka gyaan sunane ke liye prathvee kee chhor se ai, aur dekho, yahan vah haai jo sulaaiman se bhee bada haai.
jo jhaadiyon men boya gaya, yah vah haai, jo vachan ko sunata haai, par is sansar kee chinta aur dhan ka dhaekha vachan ko dabata haai, aur vah fal naheen lata.
unhon ne us se kaha, han us ne un se kaha, isaaliye har ek shaasree jo svarga ke rajy ka chela bana haai, us grahasth ke saman haai jo apane bhndar se nai aur puranee vastuen nikalata haai..
us samay nav jheel ke beech laharon se dgamaga rahee thee, kyonki hava samhane kee thee.
par jo kuchh munh se nikalata haai, vah man se nikalata haai, aur vahee manushy ko ashuuddh karata haai.
kya tum ab tak naheen samajhe? aur un panch hajar kee panch rottee smaran naheen karate, aur n yah ki kitanee ttokaariyan uttain theen?
us ne uttr diya, ki eliyyah to aega: aur sab kuchh sudhaarega.
aeesa hee tumhare pita kee jo svarga men haai yah ichchha nahee, ki in chhotton men se aek bhee nash ho.
aur maain tum se kahata hoo, ki jo koi vyabhaichar ko chhod aur kisee karan se apanee patnee ko tyagakar, doosaree se byah kare, vah vyabhaichar karata haai: aur jo chhodee hui ko byah kare, vah bhee vyabhaichar karata haai.
aur ujjaiyah se yotam utpann hua aur yotam se ahaj utpann hua aur ahaj se hijaakiyyah utpann hua.
jo tera haai, utta le, aur chala ja meree ichchha yah haai ki jitana tujhe, utana hee is pichhle ko bhee doon.
jab us ne yarooshalem men pravesh kiya, to sare nagar men halachal mach gai aur log kahane lage, yah kaun haai?
isaliye jab dakh kee baree ka svamee aaega, to un kisanon ke sath kya karega?
ki he guroo moosa ne kaha tha, ki yadi koi bina santan mar jaa, to usaka bhai us kee patnee ko byah karake apane bhai ke liye vansh utpann kare.
parantu, tum rabbee n kahalana kayonki tumhara aek hee guroo haai: aur tum sab bhai ho.
