aur naye manushyatv ko pahin lo, jo parameshvar ke anusar saty kee dhaarmikata, aur pavitrata men sraja gaya haai..
he paatnaiyo, apane apane pati ke aeese adhaeen raho, jaaise prabhu ke.
aur mere liye bhee, ki mujhe bolane ke samay aeesa prabal vachan diya jaa, ki maain hiyav se susamachar ka bhed bata sakoon jis ke liye maain janjeer se jakada hua rajadoot hoon.
aur isaliye ki mujhe is ka bhrosa haai so maain janata hoon ki maain jeeavit rahoonga, baran tum sab ke sath rahoonga jis se tum vishvas men draddh hote jao aur us men anandait raho.
par maain ne ipadeetus ko jo mera bhai, aur sahakarmee aur sangee yoddha aur tumhara doot, aur avashyak baton men meree seva tthal karanevala haai, tumhare pas bhejana avashy samajha.
prabhu men sada anandait raho maain fir kahata hoo, anaandait raho.
aur us kee maahima kee shaaktai ke anusar sab prakar kee samarth se balavant hote jao, yahan tak ki anand ke sath har prakar se dhaeeraj aur sahanashaeelata dikha sako.
aur usee ke sath bapaatisma men gade gaa, aur usee men parameshvar kee shaktai par vishvas karake, jis ne us ko mare huon men se jilaya, usake sath jee bhee utte.
he paatiyo, apanee apanee patnee se praem rakho, aur un se kattorata n karo.
jo nirdosh aur aek hee patnee ke paati ho, jin ke ladkebale vishvasee ho, aur jinhen luchapan aur nirankushata ka dosh naheen.
to us ne hamara uddhar kiya: aur yah dharma ke kamon ke karan nahee, jo ham ne ap kia, par apanee daya ke anusar, naae janm ke snan, aur pavitra atma ke hamen naya banane ke dara hua.
he bhai yah anand mujhe prabhu men teree or se mile : maseeh men mere jee ko hara bhra kar de.
aur aek doosare ke sath ikattha hona ne chhode, jaaise ki kitanon kee reeti haai, par aek doosare ko samajhate rahen aur jyon jyon us din ko nikatt ate dekho, tyon tyon aur bhee aadhaik yah kiya karo..
par ve aek uttm arthata svargeey desh ke aabhailashaee haai, isee liye parameshvar un ka parameshvar kahalane men un se naheen lajata, so us ne un ke liye aek nagar taaiyar kiya haai..
kyonaki prabhu, jis se praem karata haai, us kee tadna bhee karata haai aur jise putra bana leta haai, us ko kode bhee lagata haai.
jo tumhare aguve the, aur jinhon ne tumhen parameshvar ka vachan sunaya haai, unhen smaran rakho aur dhyan se un ke chala-chalan ka ant dekhkar un ke vishvas ka anukaran karo.
aur too unhen chadar kee nain lapettega, aur ve vasr kee nai badal jaaenge: par too vahee haai aur tere vasharen ka ant n hoga.
is karan maain us samay ke logon se rootta raha, aur kaha, ki in ke man sada bhttkate rahate haai, aur inhon ne mere magorn ko naheen paahichana.
vaaise hee maseeh ne bhee mahayajak banane kee badai apane ap se naheen lee, par us ko usee ne dee, jis ne us se kaha tha, ki too mera putra haai, aj maain hee ne tujhe janmaya haai.
yah maalikisidak shaalem ka raja, aur paramapradhaan parameshvar ka yajak, sarvada yajak bana rahata haai jab ibraaheem rajaon ko marakar lautta jata tha, to isee ne us se bhentt karake use ashaeesh dee.
kyonaki har aek mahayajak bhent, aur baalidan chaddhane ke liye ttharaya jata haai, is karan avashy haai, ki is ke pas bhee kuchh chaddhane ke liye ho.
aur kaha, ki yah us vacha ka lohoo haai, jis kee agyaa parameshvar ne tumhare liye dee haai.
parantu vachan par chalanevale bano, aur keval sunanevale hee naheen jo apane ap ko dhaekha dete haain.
vaaise hee rahab veshya bhee jab us ne dooton ko apane ghar men utara, aur doosare marga se vida kiya, to kya karmon se dhaaarmik n ttharee?
he bhaiyo, aek doosare kee badanamee n karo, jo apane bhai kee badanamee karata haai, ya bhai par dosh lagata haai, vah vyavastha kee badanamee karata haai, aur vyavastha par dosh lagata haai, to too vyavastha par chalanevala nahee, par us par hakim tthara.
kyonaki kitane aeese manushy chupake se ham men a mile haai, jin se is dand ka varnn purane samay men paahile hee se likha gaya tha: ye bhktaiheen haai, aur hamare parameshvar ke anugrah ko luchapan men badal dalate haai, aur hamare advait svamee aur prabhu yeeshu maseeh ka inkar karate haain..
aur maain ne svargadoot ke pas jakar kaha, yah chhottee pustak mujhe de aur us ne mujh se kaha le ise kha jo, aur yah tera pett kadva to karegee, par tere munh men madha see meettee lagegee.
aur vah bada ajagar arthata vahee purana sanp, jo ibalees aur shautan kahalata haai, aur sare sansar ka bhramanevala haai, prathvee par gira diya gaya aur usake doot usake sath gira diae gaae.
ye ve haai, jo striayon ke sath ashuuddh naheen hua, par kunvare haain: ye ve hee haai, ki jahan kaheen memna jata haai, ve usake peechhe ho lete haain: ye to parameshvar ke nimitt pahile fal hone ke liye manushyon men se mol liae gaae haain.
kyonaki unhon ne pavitra logo, aur bhvishyadvktaon ko lohoo bahaya tha, aur too ne unhen lohoo pilaya kyonki ve isee yogy haain.
fir us ne mujh se kaha, ki jo panee too ne dekhe, jin par veshya baaittee haai, ve log, aur bheed aur jaatiya, aur bhasha haain.
fir doosaree bar unhon ne haallailooyyah kaha: aur usake jalane ka dhauan yuganuyug uttta rahega.
aur maain ne use jo mujh se bol raha tha dekhne ke liye apana munh faera aur peechhe ghoomakar maain ne sone kee sat deevatten dekhee.
jo jay paa, vahee un vastuon ka vaaris hoga aur maain usaka parameshvar hounga, aur vah mera putra hoga.
fir us ne mujh se kaha, is pustak kee bhavishyadvvanee kee baton ko band mat kara kyonki samay nikatt haai..
maain tere kamo, aur praem, aur vishvas, aur seva, aur dhaeeraj ko janata hoo, aur yah bhee ki tere pichhle kam pahilon se baddhkar haain.
dek, maain dar par khda hua khttkhttata hoon yadi koi mera shabd sunakar dar kholega, to maain usake pas bheetar akar usake sath bhojan karoonga, aur vah mere sath.
aur jab us ne doosaree muhar kholee, to maain ne doosare praanee ko yah kahate suna, ki a.
ve fir bookhe aur pyase n honge: or n un par dhoop, n koi tapan padegee.
aur faaujon ke savaron kee ginatee bees karod thee maain ne un kee ginatee sunee.
